20health%20equity%20at%20Purdue%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20it%20replicates%2C%20the%20more%20chances%20it%20has%20to%20mutate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20multi-state%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fraw-farm-milk-california-tests-positive-bird-flu-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edairy%20cattle%20outbreak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20started%20in%20Texas%2C%20has%20infected%20865%20herds%20across%2016%20states%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CDC%2C%20and%20has%20led%20to%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20human%20cases%20among%20US%20dairy%20and%20poultry%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CDC%20has%20thus%20far%20confirmed%2061%20reported%20human%20cases%20and%20seven%20probable%20cases%20across%20the%20US%2C%20though%20some%20scientists%20estimate%20that%20the%20real%20number%20of%20infections%20is%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20half%20of%20the%20human%20cases%20are%20tied%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbird-flu-cows-milk-spread-study-suggests-how-to-stop-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteraction%20with%20sick%20cattle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20remaining%20infections%20have%20been%20traced%20to%20exposure%20to%20sick%20poultry%20or%20have%20an%20unknown%20origin%2C%20the%20CDC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20illustration%20of%20milk%20to%20be%20tested%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67635fd66c531c315b892c51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20U.S.%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20this%20month%20issued%20a%20federal%20order%20that%20requires%20the%20testing%20of%20the%20nation's%20milk%20supply.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226391b31d-a415-453e