major%20human%20outbreak%3Cspan%3E%20was%20%26quot%3Blarge%2C%20plausible%2C%20and%20imminent%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20inevitable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20that%20paper%20was%20published%20in%20early%20June%2C%20there%20had%20only%20been%20three%20confirmed%20human%20cases%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInfluenza%20has%20always%20been%20a%20concern%20for%20decades%20and%20decades%2C%20and%20this%20particular%20form%20of%20influenza%20for%20at%20least%20two%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Dye%20said.%20Bird%20flu%2C%20he%20added%2C%20has%20%26quot%3Brisen%20to%20a%20level%20of%20concern%2C%20I%20think%2C%20which%20is%20greater%20than%20ever%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-governor-declares-proactive-state-of-emergency-bird-flu-virus-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734563253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676339705cddac6581d6d1cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-governor-declares-proactive-state-of-emergency-bird-flu-virus-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20H5N1%20bird-flu%20virus%20has%20been%20found%20in%20new%20dairy-cattle%20herds%20in%20Southern%20California.%20No%20human-to-human%20spread%20has%20been%20documented.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmcfalljohnsen%40businessinsider.com%20(Morgan%20McFall-Johnsen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-governor-declares-proactive-state-of-emergency-bird-flu-virus-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Entitled%20to%20relief'%3A%20Mallya%20reacts%20to%20Nirmala's%20Rs%2014%2C131%20cr%20debt%20recovery%20remarks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734563067000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.c