off%20your%20ceiling.%20This%20means%20that%20audio%20effects%20can%20sound%20like%20they're%20coming%20from%20all%20around%20the%20room%2C%20including%20above%20your%20head.%20In%20my%20tests%2C%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20delivered%20an%20incredibly%20immersive%20experience%2C%20whether%20watching%20movies%20or%20listening%20to%20music.%20The%20sound%20is%20so%20expansive%20that%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20believing%20it%20all%20came%20from%20just%20one%20device%20under%20my%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Sonos%20Arc%20Ultra%20soundbar%20on%20a%20media%20console%20under%20a%20Samsung%20%20Frame%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67630d5b0a6d56a4f9c1e083%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sonos%20Arc%20Ultra%20is%20the%20brand's%20biggest%20and%20most%20powerful%20soundbar.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20Arc%20Ultra's%20secret%20ingredients%20is%20its%20new%20Sound%20Motion%20driver.%20This%20component%20packs%20multiple%20woofers%20into%20a%20compact%20space%2C%20offering%20deeper%20bass%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsonos-arc-soundbar-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20Arc%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20making%20the%20soundbar%20any%20larger%20in%20size.%20While%20the%20Sound%20Motion%20driver%20can't%20quite%20match%20the%20performance%20of%20a%20dedicated%20subwoofer%2C%20it%20does%20give%20movies%20and%20shows%20more%20low-end%20presence%20and%20depth%20with%20a%20full%2C%20rich%20quality%20that%20few%20stand-alone%20soundbars%20can%20beat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Arc%20Ultra%20also%20has%20exceptional%20dialogue%20clarity.%20The%20device%20offers%20an%20optional%20speech%20enhancement%20mode%2C%20but%20I%20rarely%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20it%20because%20the%20bar's%20internal%20drivers%20are%20already%20so%20well-tuned%20for%20delivering%20clear%20speech.%20If%20you%20do%20find%20yourself%20needing%20an%20extra%20boost%2C%20the%20speech%20enhancement%20emphasizes%20dialogue%20even%20more%20without%20muddying%20explosions%20or%20altering%20other%20sound%20effects.%20It's%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20downside%2C%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20is%20Sonos'%20most%20expensive%20soundbar%2C%20and%20it's%20disappointing%20that%20it%20doesn't%20support%20DTS%3AX%2C%20another%203D%20audio%20format%20that%20rivals%20Dolby%20Atmos.%20It%20also%20lacks%20HDMI%20video%20passthrough%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20use%20the%20bar%20to%20route%20extra%20devices%20to%20your%20TV%2C%20like%20a%20gaming%20console%20or%20streaming%20player.%20But%20these%20shortcomings%20are%20small%20compared%20to%20all%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20gets%20right.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20single%2C%20powerful%20speaker%20in%20your%20living%20room%20that's%20capable%20of%20handling%20all%20your%20home%20theater%20needs%2C%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20is%20the%20best%20Sonos%20soundbar%20there%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsonos-arc-ultra-soundbar-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESonos%20Arc%20Ultra%20soundbar%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-soundbar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20soundbars%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288a60d5c-4e2d-46d0-b0f9-735842308f7e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20on%20a%20budget%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20on%20a%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sonos%20Ray%20is%20the%20brand's%20most%20affordable%20and%20compact%20soundbar.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20minimal%20footprint%2C%20it's%20the%20best%20Sonos%20soundbar%20for%20bedrooms%20and%20apartments.%20For%20comparison%2C%20it's%20less%20than%20half%20the%20width%20of%20the%20Arc%20Ultra%20and%20a%20few%20inches%20shorter%20and%20less%20deep%20than%20the%20Beam%20(Gen%202).%20Despite%20its%20stature%2C%20it%20still%20far%20outdoes%20the%20capabilities%20of%20most%20speakers%20embedded%20in%20TV%20sets%2C%20especially%20lower-end%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20audio%20quality%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20a%20smooth%20experience%20that%20will%20bring%20any%20movie%20to%20life.%20You%20won't%20get%20the%20window-rattling%20lows%20or%20all%20of%20the%20flourishes%20offered%20on%20Sonos'%20pricier%20soundbars%2C%20but%20the%20Ray%20is%20impressive%20for%20its%20size%2C%20with%20a%20surprisingly%20detailed%20sound%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Sonos%20Ray%20soundbar%20resting%20on%20a%20media%20console.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67633b96b1d5f0276b36ccea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sonos%20Ray%20delivers%20more%20expansive%20sound%20than%20we%20expected%20from%20such%20a%20small%20device.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStreaming%20music%20on%20the%20Ray%20over%20WiFi%20is%20great%2C%20too%2C%20offering%20better%20quality%20than%20a%20Bluetooth%20connection%20would%20provide.%20That%20said%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bummer%20that%20Sonos%20doesn't%20also%20include%20Bluetooth%20support%20as%20an%20alternative%20for%20those%20instances%20when%20WiFi%20might%20not%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ray%20is%20also%20a%20bit%20lacking%20in%20wired%20connectivity.%20It%20doesn't%20include%20an%20HDMI%20port%20and%20can%20only%20connect%20to%20a%20TV%20(or%20PC)%20via%20an%20optical%20cable.%20This%20does%20mean%20it%20has%20wide%20compatibility%20among%20older%20televisions%2C%20but%20it%20also%20means%20that%20it%20doesn't%20support%20lossless%20audio%20formats%2C%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20or%20automatic%20pairing%20with