a%3E%20pose%20more%20uncertainty%20to%20the%20US%20economy%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president-elect%20has%20suggested%20he%20would%20impose%20broad%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20key%20trading%20partners%20with%20the%20US%2C%20including%20China%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Canada%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20higher%20prices%20for%20imported%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20Powell%20said%20there%20is%20too%20much%20uncertainty%20around%20Trump's%20trade%20plans%20to%20make%20any%20concrete%20predictions%20about%20next%20year's%20policy%20decisions%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20don't%20know%20really%20very%20much%20at%20all%20about%20the%20actual%20policy%2C%20so%20it's%20very%20premature%20to%20try%20to%20make%20any%20kind%20of%20conclusion%2C%26quot%3B%20Powell%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20what%20will%20be%20tariffed%2C%20from%20what%20countries%2C%20for%20how%20long%2C%20in%20what%20size.%20We%20don't%20know%20whether%20there'll%20be%20retaliatory%20tariffs.%20We%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20transmission%20of%20any%20of%20that%20will%20be%20into%20consumer%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Powell%20said%20some%20FOMC%20members%20did%20consider%20fiscal%20policy%2C%20like%20tariffs%2C%20in%20their%20economic%20predictions%2C%20showing%20how%20the%20Fed%20is%20facing%20a%20range%20of%20uncertain%20scenarios%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20once%20Trump%20unveils%20his%20policies%2C%20the%20Fed%20would%20consider%20any%20necessary%20changes%20to%20its%20policy%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20just%20not%20at%20that%20stage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Powell%20has%20reiterated%20that%20the%20Fed%20should%20move%20more%20cautiously%20instead%20of%20risking%20cutting%20rates%20prematurely%20and%20having%20to%20course%20correct%20later%20on.%20That's%20still%20the%20Fed's%20outlook%20going%20into%20the%20new%20year%20as%20the%20central%20bank%20continues%20its%20goal%20of%20reaching%202%25%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20economic%20progress%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Powell%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-november-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20coming%20down%20at%20a%20slower%20pace%20than%20the%20Fed%20would%20prefer.%20The%20consumer%20price%20index%2C%20which%20measures%20inflation%2C%20rose%202.7%25%20year-over-year%20in%20November%2C%20a%20slight%20uptick%20from%20the%202.6%25%20reading%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20path%20is%20uncertain%2C%20you%20go%20a%20little%20bit%20slower%2C%26quot%3B%20Powell%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20unlike%20driving%20on%20a%20foggy%20night%20or%20walking%20into%20a%20dark%20room%20full%20of%20furniture%2C%20you%20just%20slow%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-many-interest-rate-cuts-next-year-trump-tariffs-uncertainty-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734557371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6763328e6c531c315b891e18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-many-interest-rate-cuts-next-year-trump-tariffs-uncertainty-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20cut%20interest%20rates%20in%20its%20final%20decision%20of%20the%20year%2C%20Powell%20said%20tariffs%20could%20add%20uncertainty%20to%20the%20central%20bank's%20plans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-many-interest-rate-cuts-next-year-trump-tariffs-uncertainty-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At