-fe0c-4e28-8302-200270b11952%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESituation%20analysis%3A%20What%20problem%20was%20the%20company%20trying%20to%20solve%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Emergency%20Number%20Association%20estimates%20that%20240%20million%20911%20calls%20are%20made%20in%20the%20US%20each%20year.%20But%20fragmented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femergency-response-call-centers-using-ai-cloud-technology-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemergency-response%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20various%20agencies%20and%20organizations%20can%20lead%20to%20dangerous%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20hope%20to%20never%20call%20911%2C%20but%20when%20you%20do%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Jehan%20Wickramasuriya%2C%20the%20corporate%20vice%20president%20of%20AI%20and%20platforms%20at%20Motorola%20Solutions%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20call%20takers'%20jobs%20can%20be%20demanding%20and%20unpredictable%2C%20and%20they're%20often%20under%20intense%20pressure.%20%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20a%20high%20level%20of%20stress%20if%20there's%20an%20active%20shooter%20or%20domestic%20disturbance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20keep%20a%20caller%20calm%20and%20simultaneously%20find%20out%20if%20they%20need%20medical%20help.%26quot%3B%20Meanwhile%2C%20he%20said%2C%20callers%20may%20be%20%26quot%3Bspeaking%20so%20fast%20that%20it's%20difficult%20to%20understand%20and%20retain%20everything%20they%20say.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224736%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Jehan%20Wickramasuriya%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6762030d1d90e3bcf31d78af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJehan%20Wickramasuriya%20is%20the%20corporate%20vice%20president%20of%20AI%20and%20platforms%20at%20Motorola%20Solutions.%3Cp%3EMotorola%20Solutions%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPinpointing%20a%20caller's%20location%20adds%20a%20layer%20of%20complexity.%20Mobile%20911%20calls%20are%20typically%20routed%20based%20on%20cell-tower%20locations%20rather%20than%20the%20caller's%20actual%20position.%20This%20requires%20calls%20to%20be%20redirected%2C%20adding%20several%20seconds%20to%20response%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20it's%20a%20data%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Wickramasuriya%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20needs%20to%20get%20transmitted%20in%20each%20call.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMotorola%20Solutions%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20consolidate%20this%20data%20in%20a%20single%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f20a1a3d-04da-4e9e-b92d-f0427ffc4466%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20staff%20and%20stakeholders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20structures%20its%20AI%20research%20team%20around%20specialized%20AI%20domains%2C%20such%20as%20computer%20vision%20and%20speech%20and%20audio%20processing%2C%20rather%20than%20individual%20product%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWickramasuriya%20said%20the%20core%20AI%20team%20consisted%20of%20about%2050%20scientists%2C%20developers%2C%20and%20engineers%20who%20collaborate%20closely%20with%20hundreds%20of%20product%20managers%2C%20designers%2C%20and%20user-experience%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMotorola%20Solutions%20also%20works%20with%20various%20cloud%20and%20technology%20vendors%20on%20its%20AI-enabled%20products%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22acb68d11-ba5f-4f91-bb07-c9501961474c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20in%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Motorola%20Solutions%20launched%20Vesta%20NXT%2C%20software%20designed%20to%20help%20911%20call%20handlers%20manage%20emergency%20calls.%20It%20brings%20data%20from%20various%20public-safety%20systems%20onto%20one%20platform%2C%20helping%20the%20handlers%20gather%20and%20summarize%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20uses%20AI%20to%20surface%20details%20including%20the%20caller's%20location%20and%2C%20for%20callers%20who%20have%20opted%20to%20share%20their%20medical%20profile%20from%20their%20phone%2C%20any%20underlying%20health%20conditions.%20It%20can%20also%20suggest%20the%20best%20entrance%20to%20a%20building.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20important%20information%20for%20first%20responders%2C%26quot%3B%20Wickramasuriya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20has%20translation%20and%20transcription%20capabilities%2C%20helping%20English%20speakers%20and%20non-English%20speakers%20communicate.%20AI%20also%20helps%20call%20handlers%20manage%20nonemergency%20calls%20%E2%80%94%20by%20streamlining%20the%20reporting%20of%20issues%20like%20abandoned%20cars%20or%20stolen%20property%2C%20call%20handlers%20can%20focus%20more%20on%20critical%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20important%2C%20AI%20can%20improve%20the%20human%20element%20of%20emergency%20response.%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20working%20in%20the%20background%20to%20help%20the%20call%20taker%20attend%20to%20the%20person%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Wickramasuriya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22251d837d-e226-42fc-a2f0-5055ffbccfd2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMotorola%20Solutions%20says%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20911%20call%20centers%20in%20the%20US%20use%20its%20call-handling%20software.%20It's%20transitioning%20existing%20Vesta%20911%20users%20to%20its%20new%20system%20with%20the%20AI%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20says%20these%20AI%20tools%20are%20already%20translating%20millions%20of%20minutes%20of%20audio%20each%20month%20and%20have%20helped%20lighten%20emergency-call%20handlers'%20workloads%20partly%20by%20resolving%20nonemergency%20calls%20and%20connecting%20callers%20to%20other%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELee%20County%20is%20the%20first%20Public%20Safety%20Answering%20Point%2C%20which%20is%20a%20call%20center%20that%20handles%20emergency%20calls%20and%20coordinates%20responses%2C%20to%20use%20the%20VESTA%20NXT.%20Motorola%20Solutions%20said%20administrators%20there%20found%20the%20AI-generated%20searchable%20text%20transcripts%20and%20real-time%20summaries%20of%20911%20calls%20that%20call%20handlers%20can%20share%20with%20dispatchers%20and%20first%20responders%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.motorolasolutions.com%2Fen_us%2Fassist-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehelped%20save%20time%20and%20alleviate%20stress%20for%20call%20handlers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275929f0d-dd76-46f9-82c0-d3782f0329c2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWickramasuriya%20said%20the%20company%20was%20focused%20on%20improving%20Vesta%20NXT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20goal%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bexpand%20the%20usefulness%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20software%20by%20integrating%20it%20more%20deeply%20into%20existing%20workflows%2C%20including%20by%20developing%20features%20that%20connect%20first%20responders%20directly%20with%20dispatchers%20and%20call%20takers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20aim%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20to%20help%20understaffed%20911%20call%20centers%20%26quot%3Bunderstand%20their%20staffing%20needs%20and%20identify%20which%20call%20takers%20are%20handling%20high-stress%20situations%20and%20address%20stress%20and%20fatigue%20among%20call%20handlers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmotorola-solutions-using-ai-improve-911-call-response-times-data-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734556807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67620540ccd