just%20riding%20the%20high%20wave%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20business%2C%20he%20is%20now%20doing%20the%20same%20in%20geopolitics.%20Having%20being%20included%20in%20the%20Trump%20Administration%202.0%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20finds%20himself%20immersed%20in%20the%20world%20of%20politics.%20Though%20he%20was%20deeply%20involved%20with%20Donald%20Trump's%20campaign%20and%20is%20partially%20credited%20for%20the%20latter's%20win%20in%20the%20US%20elections%2C%20he%20now%20seems%20to%20be%20backing%20-%20or%20rather%2C%20influencing%20-%20leaders%20from%20beyond%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20DONE%2C%20MUSK%20SETS%20EYES%20ON%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20supporting%20one%20firebrand%20leader%20to%20now%20backing%20another%20one%20-%20this%20time%20in%20the%20UK%20-%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20held%20extensive%20talks%20with%20anti-immigration%20hardliner%20Nigel%20Farage.%20The%20discussions%20between%20the%20two%20were%20largely%20focused%20on%20Musk%20funding%20Farage's%20hard-right%20party%20'Reform%20UK'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20who%20now%20freely%20uses%20Donald%20Trump's%20Florida%20resort%20estate-cum-residence%2C%20Mar-a-Lago%2C%20as%20his%20political%20office%2C%20invited%20Nigel%20Farage%20for%20a%20meeting%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriting%20about%20it%20in%20British%20daily%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F12%2F17%2Felon-musk-believes-britain-is-in-very-deep-trouble%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Farage%20confirmed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20issue%20of%20money%20was%20discussed%26quot%3B%2C%20though%20the%20two%20could%20not%20agree%20on%20the%20amount%20in%20question%20by%20the%20end%20of%20that%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20ongoing%20negotiations%20on%20that%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Farage%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20details%20about%20the%20meeting%2C%20that%20will%20most%20certainly%20raise%20eyebrows%20in%20the%20UK's%20two%20main%20political%20party%20offices%20-%20The%20Labour%20Party%2C%20now%20in%20government%20and%20the%20Conservative%20Party%2C%20currently%20the%20opposition%20-%20Mr%20Farage%20mentioned%20about%20Elon%20Musk's%20disdain%20for%20both%20parties.%20He%20stated%20that%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bdescribed%20the%20Labour%20and%20Conservative%20parties%20as%20the%20uniparty%2C%20and%20left%20us%20(Reform%20Party)%20in%20no%20doubt%20that%20he%20is%20right%20behind%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20article%20Mr%20Farage%20also%20mentioned%20that%20he%20aims%20to%20learn%20from%20Elon%20Musk's%20cash%20incentives%20for%20people%20to%20be%20encouraged%20to%20vote%C2%A0%20-%20a%20strategy%20that%20worked%20for%20Donald%20Trump's%20Republican%20party%20during%20the%20US%20elections.%20Mr%20Farage%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20home%20with%20copious%20notes%20on%20how%20they%20increased%20turnout%2C%20voter%20registration%2C%20and%20so%20much%20more%2C%20and%20all%20of%20this%20I%20intend%20to%20implement%20as%20part%20of%20the%20professionalisation%20of%20our%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20reportedly%20considering%20an%20initial%20donation%20of%20%24100%20million%20to%20Nigel%20Farage's%20Reform%20Party.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20BBC%2C%20Mr%20Farage%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20wants%20to%20help%20us%2C%20he's%20not%20opposed%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20us%20money%20provided%20we%20can%20do%20it%20legally%20through%20UK%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20a%20steep%20ask%20for%20Mr%20Farage's%20party%20to%20even%20think%20of%20winning%20a%20general%20election%20in%20the%20UK.%20In%20the%20most%20recent%20elections%20held%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Reform%20Party%20won%20just%20five%20seats%20in%20the%20650-seat%20UK%20Parliament.%20However%2C%20it%20scores%20impressively%20in%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20accounting%20for%2014%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20the%20votes%20cast.%20Mr%20Farage%20hopes%20that%20with%20Musk's%20support%20-%20moral%20and%20financial%20-%20his%20party%20might%20just%20do%20the%20unthinkable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcluding%20his%20article%2C%20Mr%20Farage%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20heartening%20to%20listen%20to%20Elon%20speak%20about%20UK%20politics%20with%20such%20deep%20care.%20He%20regards%20the%20mother%20country%20of%20the%20English-speaking%20world%20as%20being%20in%20very%20deep%20trouble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Farage%20wrote%20on%20Musk's%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20that%20%26quot%3B%26quot%3BBritain%20needs%20reform%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20which%20Elon%20Musk%20promptly%20replied%20%26quot%3BAbsolutely%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAbsolutely%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1869034409799950394%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EELON%20MUSK'S%20CALL%20WITH%20UKRAINE'S%20ZELENSKY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20Elon%20Musk%20was%20with%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20President-elect's%20residence%20and%20luxury%20resort%20Mar-a-Lago%20in%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida%20when%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Ukraine's%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20spoke%20on%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20phone%20call%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20reportedly%20handed%20the%20phone%20over%20to%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20supposedly%20asked%20the%20SpaceX%20founder%20to%20join%20the%20call%20with%20President%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg