0report%20by%20CNN%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20other%20world%20leaders%20-%20for%20geopolitical%20reasons%20as%20well%20as%20for%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20time%20will%20unravel%20whether%20Elon%20Musk's%20political%20outreach%20is%20restricted%20to%20just%20pulling%20a%20few%20strings%2C%20or%20will%20it%20result%20in%20him%20holding%20on%20to%20the%20very%20reins%20that%20might%20restructure%20global%20politics.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734550620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fvvhbh134_elon-musk-reuters_625x300_29_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-leaders-on-speed-dial-how-elon-musk-is-causing-geopolitical-tremors-7280783%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20isn't%20unthinkable%20that%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%20can%20pull%20more%20than%20just%20a%20few%20strings%20with%20top%20politicians%2C%20but%20Elon%20Musk%20seems%20to%20be%20investing%20himself%20in%20the%20political%20world%20with%20such%20intensity%20that%20analysts%20now%20wonder%20if%20there's%20a%20larger%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-leaders-on-speed-dial-how-elon-musk-is-causing-geopolitical-tremors-7280783%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20eased%20LAC%20build-up%3A%20Pentagon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734550181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116451689%2Cimgsize-1419707.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fchina-hasnt-eased-lac-build-up-pentagon%2Farticleshow%2F116449204.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RAJAT%20PANDIT%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fchina-hasn