0level%20meet%20since%20the%20flare-up%20of%20incidents%20at%20the%20border.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20follows%20the%20bilateral%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20held%20in%20Kazan%20last%20month.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20significant%20breakthough%20amid%20the%20chill%20that%20had%20set%20in%20following%20the%20clashes%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20--%20the%20worst%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20meet%20was%20meant%20to%20oversee%20the%20management%20of%20peace%20at%20the%20border%20and%20explore%20a%20%26quot%3Bfair%2C%20reasonable%20and%20mutually%20acceptable%20solution%20to%20the%20boundary%20question%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meet%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20continue%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20maintain%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20and%20promote%20the%20healthy%20and%20stable%20development%20of%20bilateral%20relations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20discussions%20both%20SRs%20also%20underlined%20the%20importance%20of%20maintaining%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20to%20promote%20overall%20development%20of%20the%20India-China%20bilateral%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20reaffirmed%20their%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%20to%20continue%20seeking%20a%20fair%2C%20reasonable%20and%20mutually%20acceptable%20package%20solution%20to%20the%20boundary%20issue%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20political%20guidelines%20agreed%20upon%20by%20the%20special%20representatives%20of%20the%20two%20countries%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20things%20the%20two%20sides%20also%20agreed%20to%20further%20refine%20the%20management%20and%20control%20rules%20in%20the%20border%20area%2C%20strengthen%20the%20building%20of%20confidence-building%20measures%2C%20and%20achieve%20sustainable%20peace%20and%20tranquility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cross-border%20exchanges%20and%20cooperation%20will%20be%20strengthened%20and%20Indian%20pilgrims'%20pilgrimage%20to%20Kailash-Mansarovar%2C%20Tibet%2C%20China%2C%20cross-border%20river%20cooperation%20and%20Nathu%20La%20border%20trade%20will%20be%20resumed%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20hold%20a%20new%20round%20of%20special%20representatives'%20meetings%20in%20India%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disengagement%2C%20finalised%20in%20October%2C%20saw%20both%20India%20and%20China%20pull%20back%20troops%20from%20the%20two%20remaining%20friction%20points%20in%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang%2C%20after%20nearly%20four%20years%20of%20military%20standoff%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20disengagement%2C%20both%20India%20and%20China%20are%20keen%20to%20build%20on%20this%20momentum%20and%20re-establish%20trust.%20The%20special%20representatives'%20talks%2C%20which%20are%20part%20of%20a%20long-established%20mechanism%20to%20address%20the%20border%20dispute%2C%20have%20been%20convened%20after%20a%20hiatus%2C%20with%20the%20last%20meeting%20held%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734548040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fm3s7m9o8_ajit-doval-wang-yi_625x300_18_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-china-arrive-at-6-consensus-points-as-ajit-doval-wang-yi-meet-7279709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20China%20agreed%20on%20six%20points%20to%20resolve%20the%20border%20issue%20as%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20met%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Passengers%20Panic%2C%20Scream%20For%20Help%20As%20Ferry%20Sinks%20Off%20Mumbai%20Coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20India