2Fmsid-116445318%2Cimgsize-24018.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-yash-chopras-actress-sonam-khan-got-slapped-by-her-mother-for-doing-a-bold-photoshoot%2Farticleshow%2F116445318.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116445318.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESonam%20Khan%2C%20launched%20by%20Yash%20Chopra%2C%20recalled%20a%20bold%20photoshoot%20from%20her%20early%20career%20that%20angered%20her%20mother.%20The%20shoot%2C%20featuring%20Sonam%20in%20a%20short%20dress%20hidden%20by%20tall%20grass%2C%20resulted%20in%20a%20slap%20and%20a%20torn%20magazine.%20Despite%20her%20parents'%20protectiveness%2C%20Sonam%20maintained%20her%20rebellious%20spirit%20throughout%20her%20Bollywood%20journey%2C%20starring%20in%20hits%20like%20Tridev%20and%20Kroadh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-yash-chopras-actress-sonam-khan-got-slapped-by-her-mother-for-doing-a-bold-photoshoot%2Farticleshow%2F116445318.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Mukadma%2C%20Ilzam'%20%3A%20Rajasthan%20To%20Change%20Urdu%20Words%20In%20Policing%20To%20Hindi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMukadma%20(case)%2C%20Mulzim%20(accused)%2C%20Ilzam%20(allegation)%2C%20Ittila%20(information)%2C%20Chashmdeed%20(eyewitness)%20and%20many%20such%20terms%20may%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20policing%20vocabulary%20in%20Rajasthan%20for%20long%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20issuing%20direction%20to%20replace%20them%20with%20appropriate%20Hindi%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20police%20headquarters%20started%20the%20exercise%20following%20a%20letter%20by%20Minister%20of%20State%20(Home)%20Jawahar%20Singh%20Bedham%2C%20seeking%20information%20about%20such%20words%20and%20their%20Hindi%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20letter%2C%20state%20police%20chief%20U%20R%20Sahoo%20wrote%20to%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(Training)%20last%20month%20to%20collect%20details%20of%20Urdu%20words%20and%20find%20out%20their%20appropriate%20replacements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20he%20also%20instructed%20the%20officer%20to%20omit%20Urdu%20terms%20from%20training%20material%2C%20apprise%20all%20trainees%20of%20the%20new%20Hindi%20words%2C%20and%20disseminate%20information%20about%20the%20new%20Hindi%20words%20in%20the%20ongoing%20training%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGP's%20communication%2C%20dated%20November%2011%2C%20also%20gives%20a%20reference%20of%20the%20letter%20from%20MoS%20Bedham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EADG%20(Crime)%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20also%20wrote%20to%20all%20police%20range%20inspector%20generals%20on%20December%2010%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20DGP's%20letter.%20And%20then%2C%20letters%20were%20sent%20to%20all%20SPs%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20follow-up%20of%20the%20instructions%20from%20the%20PHQ%20(Police%20headquarters)%2C%20the%20SPs%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20collect%20information%20about%20the%20Urdu%20words%20and%20their%20Hindi%20replacements%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20criticised%20the%20government%20over%20the%20move%2C%20calling%20it%20uncalled%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaw%20and%20order%20situation%20is%20worsening%20in%20the%20state%20but%20the%20state%20government%20is%20not%20bothered%20about%20it.%20Rather%20than%20replacing%20words%20which%20have%20been%20there%20in%20practice%20for%20long%2C%20the%20government%20should%20take%20effective%20action%20to%20control%20crime%20and%20restore%20law%20and%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20se