ptable%20package%20solution%20to%20the%20boundary%20issue.%20The%20consensus%20points%20also%20include%20cross-border%20tourism%20including%20in%20areas%20like%20Tibet%20and%20cross-border%20river%20cooperation%20and%20Nathu%20La%20border%20trade%20and%20resumption%20of%20Mansarovar%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20Special-Representative%20level%20meet%20since%20the%20flare-up%20of%20incidents%20at%20the%20border.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20follows%20the%20bilateral%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20held%20in%20Kazan%20last%20month.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20significant%20breakthough%20amid%20the%20chill%20that%20had%20set%20in%20following%20the%20clashes%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20--%20the%20worst%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20meet%20was%20meant%20to%20oversee%20the%20management%20of%20peace%20at%20the%20border%20and%20explore%20a%20%26quot%3Bfair%2C%20reasonable%20and%20mutually%20acceptable%20solution%20to%20the%20boundary%20question%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meet%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20continue%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20maintain%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20and%20promote%20the%20healthy%20and%20stable%20development%20of%20bilateral%20relations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20discussions%20both%20SRs%20also%20underlined%20the%20importance%20of%20maintaining%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20to%20promote%20overall%20development%20of%20the%20India-China%20bilateral%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20reaffirmed%20their%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%20to%20continue%20seeking%20a%20fair%2C%20reasonable%20and%20mutually%20acceptable%20package%20solution%20to%20the%20boundary%20issue%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20political%20guidelines%20agreed%20upon%20by%20the%20special%20representatives%20of%20the%20two%20countries%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20things%20the%20two%20sides%20also%20agreed%20to%20further%20refine%20the%20management%20and%20control%20rules%20in%20the%20border%20area%2C%20strengthen%20the%20building%20of%20confidence-building%20measures%2C%20and%20achieve%20sustainable%20peace%20and%20tranquility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cross-border%20exchanges%20and%20cooperation%20will%20be%20strengthened%20and%20Indian%20pilgrims'%20pilgrimage%20to%20Tibet%2C%20China%2C%20cross-border%20river%20cooperation%20and%20Nathu%20La%20border%20trade%20will%20be%20resumed%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20hold%20a%20new%20round%20of%20special%20representatives'%20meetings%20in%20India%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disengagement%2C%20finalised%20in%20October%2C%20saw%20both%20India%20and%20China%20pull%20back%20troops%20from%20the%20two%20remaining%20friction%20points%20in%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang%2C%20after%20nearly%20four%20years%20of%20military%20standoff%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20disengagement%2C%20both%20India%20and%20China%20are%20keen%20to%20build%20on%20this%20momentum%20and%20re-establish%20trust.%20The%20special%20representatives'%20talks%2C%20which%20are%20part%20of%20a%20long-established%20mechanism%20to%20address%20the%20border%20dispute%2C%20have%20been%20convened%20after%20a%20hiatus%2C%20with%20the%20last%20meeting%20held%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734539940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fm3s7m9o8_ajit-doval-wang-yi_625x300_18_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-china-arrive-at-6-consensus-points-as-ajit-doval-wang-yi-meet-7279709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20China%20agreed%20on%20six%20points%20to%20resolve%20the%20border%20issue%20as%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20met%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Congress%20Workers%20Killed%20Because%20Of%20Police%20Action%2C%20Says%20Party%3B%20Cops%20Deny%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20Congress%20leaders%20died%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bpolice%20action%26quot%3B%20during%20protests%20in%20Guwahati%20and%20Lucknow%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20party%20has%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20both%20cities%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20deaths%20did%20not%20occur%20because%20of%20their%20actions%20and%20no%20injury%20marks%20were%20found%20on%20the%20two%20leaders'%20bodies.%20The%20exact%20reason%20for%20the%20deaths%2C%20they%20added%2C%20will%20be%20clear%20after%20the%20post-mortem%20is%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incidents%20took%20place%20in%20the%20two%20cities%20as%20the%20Congress%20held%20a%20nationwide%20protest%20over%20several%20issues%2C%20including%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20alleged%20government%20inaction%20over%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20a%20demand%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BTear%20Gas%20Firing%26quot%3B%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Guwahati%2C%20a%20Congress%20march%20towards%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20turned%20violent%20when%20the%20protesters%20clashed%20with%20police%2C%20who%20tried%20to%20disperse%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20leaders%2C%20including%20Assam%20Congress%20chief%20Bhupen%20Kumar%20Borah%20and%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Ripun%20Bora%2C%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20police%20and%20taken%20away%20in%20buses.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20alleged%20the%20police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells%20to%20disperse%20the%20remaining%20crowd.%20They%20said%20Mridul%20Islam%2C%20who%20was%20a%20lawyer%20and%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20state%20unit's%20legal%20cell%2C%20suffered%20injuries%20and%20was%20rushed%20to%20Guwahati%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20where%20he%20died%20of%20his%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20more%20than%208%2C000%20people%20were%20proceeding%20towards%20the%20Governor's%20House%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20the%20Assam%20Police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells.%20They%20used%20it%20thrice...%20Many%20journalists%20were%20injured.%20I%20was%20also%20injured.%20Unfortunately%2C%20one%20of%20our%20colleagues%20died%20on%20the%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Borah%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20police%20action%20on%20the%20protesters%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpre-planned%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20opposition%20party.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20pre-planned%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20Congress%20workers%20and%20create%20a%20fear%20psychosis...%20The%20Congress%20is%20not%20scared%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20Congress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20also%20condemned%20the%20%26quot%3Bbrutal%20torture%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20state%20police.%20%26quot%3BI%20condemn%20such%20actions%20of%20the%20government%20who%20do%20not%20understand%20the%20language%20of%20democratic%20protest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Facebook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuwahati%20Police%20Commissioner%20Diganta%20Barah%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20tear%20gas%20shells%20were%20not%20fired%2C%20but%20rolled.%20%26quot%3BPolice%20only%20rolled%20three%20shells%20onto%20the%20road%20so%20that%20the%20people%20would%20be%20dispersed%20by%20the%20smoke.%20The%20protesters%20took%20them%20and%20threw%20them%20at%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Barah%20also%20said%20that%20there%20were%20no%20injury%20marks%20on%20Islam's%20body.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20told%20that%20he%20complained%20of%20uneasiness%20and%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Congress%20has%20filed%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20the%20state%20police%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20using%20excessive%20force%20to%20halt%20the%20party's%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Death%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lucknow%2C%20Gorakhpur's%20Youth%20Congress%20leader%20Prabhat%20Pandey%20died%20after%20police%20allegedly%20used%20force%20to%20disperse%20the%20crowd%20that%20had%20gathered%20near%20the%20state%20assembly.%20Congress%20workers%20said%20Pandey%20died%20of%20suffocation%20after%20the%20police%20used%20force%20and%20the%20people%20in%20the%20crowd%20panicked%20and%20began%20pushing%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20chief%20Ajay%20Rai%20claimed%20that%20Pandey%20died%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bpolice%20brutality%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20while%20going%20to%20gherao%20the%20assembly%2C%20our%20young%20colleague%20Prabhat%20Pandey%20ji%20passed%20away%20due%20to%20police%20brutality%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rai%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20incident%20is%20extremely%20sad%20and%20condemnable.%20Our%20Congress%20family%20is%20hurt%20and%20angry%20by%20this%20accident.%20We%20will%20not%20tolerate%20this%20incident%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Central%20Lucknow)%20Raveena%20Tyagi%2C%20however%2C%20said%20no%20force%20was%20used%20during%20the%20protest%20and%20that%20Pandey%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20Civil%20Hospital%20in%20Hazratganj%20in%20an%20unconscious%20condition%20from%20the%20Congress%20office.%20%26quot%3BThe%20doctors%20declared%20him%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20also%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20visible%20injury%20mark%20on%20Pandey's%20body.%20%26quot%3BApart%20from%20this%2C%20a%20pos