content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20government%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20spent%20more%20than%20Rs%2032.85%20crore%20on%20air%20travel%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%20since%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20averaging%20Rs%209.25%20lakh%20a%20day.%20The%20revelation%20has%20sparked%20political%20debates%2C%20with%20critics%20questioning%20the%20fiscal%20prudence%20of%20the%20expenditure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20--%20in%20response%20to%20questions%20raised%20by%20Congress%20MLA%20Pratap%20Grewal%20--%20has%20told%20the%20assembly%20that%20Chief%20Minister%20Dr%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20ministers%2C%20and%20senior%20officials%20made%20666%20air%20trips%20using%20both%20government%20and%20private%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%20428%20were%20on%20rented%20aircraft%20and%20238%20on%20government-owned%20planes%20and%20helicopters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20private%20planes%20--%20hired%20222%20times%20--%20alone%20accounted%20for%20Rs%2036.39%20crore.%20Private%20helicopters%20were%20used%2097%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAviation%20Department%20officials%20clarified%20that%20hiring%20private%20aircraft%20becomes%20necessary%20when%20government%20planes%20are%20unavailable.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20usage%2C%20with%20minimal%20use%20by%20other%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20heavy%20reliance%20on%20rented%20aircraft%20began%20after%20the%20state%20government's%20C-90%20plane%20crashed%20at%20Gwalior%20Airport%20in%20May%202021%20during%20a%20Remdesivir%20delivery%20mission.%20The%20accident%2C%20attributed%20to%20pilot%20negligence%2C%20rendered%20the%20plane%20unusable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20state%20has%20hired%20aircraft%20regularly%20and%20plans%20to%20continue%20doing%20so%20until%20the%20new%20Challenger%203500%20jet%2C%20worth%20Rs%20234%20crore%2C%20is%20delivered%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20c