C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc89x0j1le4lo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Who%20Took%20Care%20Of%20Ambedkar's%20Legacy%3F%20PM%20Modi%20Settles%20The%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fch9teucg_pm-modi-75th-constitution-day_625x300_26_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20rotten%20ecosystem%20think%20their%20malicious%20lies%20can%20hide%20their%20misdeeds%20of%20several%20years%2C%20especially%20their%20insult%20towards%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%2C%20they%20are%20gravely%20mistaken!%20The%20people%20of%20India%20have%20seen%20time%20and%20again%20how%20one%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20one%20dynasty%2C%20has%20indulged%20in%20every%20possible%20dirty%20trick%20to%20obliterate%20the%20legacy%20of%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20and%20humiliate%20the%20SC%2FST%20communities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strong%20opening%20of%20a%20thread%20posted%20on%20X%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20sets%20the%20tone.%20He%20then%20proceeds%20to%20list%20multiple%20wrongs%20committed%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20beginning%20with%20India's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20while%20highlighting%20what%20his%20government%20has%20done%20to%20honour%20the%20memory%20of%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20carry%20forward%20his%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20fact%20that%20Ambedkar%2C%20feeling%20neglected%20as%20the%20law%20minister%20in%20Nehru's%20cabinet%2C%20resigned%20in%20September%201951.%20He%20spoke%20in%20Parliament%2C%20explaining%20why%20he%20was%20compelled%20to%20resign%20and%20how%20Prime%20Minister%20Nehru%20consistently%20sidelined%20him.%20It%20is%20also%20true%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Communists%20worked%20to%20defeat%20Ambedkar%20in%20two%20elections.%20Additionally%2C%20denying%20him%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20and%20refusing%20to%20place%20his%20portrait%20in%20Parliament's%20Central%20Hall%20were%20significant%20oversights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20facts%20that%20even%20Congress%20and%20its%20aligned%20groups%20cannot%20dispute.%20Modi%20had%20also%20touched%20upon%20these%20points%20in%20his%20concluding%20remarks%20during%20the%20two-day-long%20debate%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9CGlorious%20Journey%20of%2075%20Years%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20must%20have%20thought%20it%20prudent%20to%20make%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%20to%20clarify%20the%20issue%2C%20lest%20Congress's%20allegations%20against%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%94specifically%2C%20that%20he%20insulted%20Ambedkar%E2%80%94gain%20traction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliamentary%20election%20results%20have%20shown%20that%20issues%20related%20to%20Ambedkar%20and%20reservations%20have%20become%20highly%20sensitive.%20The%20politics%20surrounding%20these%20issues%20can%20significantly%20impact%20the%20fortunes%20of%20political%20parties.%20Modi%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20let%20the%20Congress%2C%20its%20allies%2C%20and%20associated%20groups%20dominate%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20first%20consider%20how%20it%20all%20began.%20The%20two%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20saw%20an%20impassioned%20debate%20on%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20Constitution%20on%20Friday%2C%20Saturday%2C%20Monday%2C%20and%20Tuesday.%20Several%20speakers%20deviated%20from%20the%20listed%20topic%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20encouraging%20to%20see%20Parliament%20finally%20functioning%2C%20after%20days%20of%20forced%20adjournments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20demanded%20the%20debate%20after%20the%20Constitution%20Day%20(November%2026)%2C%20which%20was%20observed%20in%20the%20Central%20Hall%20of%20the%20old%20Parliament%20House.%20The%20observance%20of%20Samvidhan%20Diwas%2C%20or%20Constitution%20Day%2C%20to%20commemorate%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20by%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%202015.%20The%20Congress%20wanted%20its%20views%20to%20be%20reflected%20and%20recorded%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20Congress's%20de%20facto%20leader%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20has%20been%20waving%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20claiming%20to%20be%20its%20protector.%20His%20sister%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20took%20her%20oath%20as%20an%20MP%20while%20holding%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20in%20one%20hand.%20The%20party's%20strategists%20must%20have%20thought%20that%20this%20would%20be%20the%20perfect%20occasion%20to%20criticise%20the%20government%20and%20its%20alleged%20assault%20on%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20was%20also%20to%20use%20the%20occasion%20as%20a%20launch%20platform%20for%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20making%20her%20parliamentary%20debut%20in%20this%20session.%20She%20was%20fielded%20as%20the%20lead%20speaker%20from%20Congress%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20debate%2C%20while%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20scheduled%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20second%20day%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20concluding%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20ruled%20the%20country%20for%20over%2055%20years%2C%20and%20its%20strategists%20just%20could%20not%20anticipate%20the%20kind%20of%20bouncers%20coming%20their%20way.%20The%20treatment%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20constitutional%20institutions%20by%20Congress's%20first%20family%E2%80%94from%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20time%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20in%201947%2C%20through%20the%20regimes%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20Rajeev%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20Manmohan%20Singh%20(when%20UPA%20chairperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20used%20to%20call%20the%20shots)%E2%80%94proved%20to%20be%20a%20sore%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20were%20well-prepared%20to%20counter%20Congress%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20its%20most%20vulnerable%20point%E2%80%94the%20first%20family.%20Anyone%20watching%20the%20debate%20could%20see%20that%20the%20speeches%20of%20PM%20Modi%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20caused%20considerable%20discomfort%20to%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies.%20The%20facts%20presented%20in%20the%20House%20were%20clearly%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20just%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20or%20the%20Home%20Minister's%20speeches%3B%20remarks%20from%20several%20BJP%20allies%2C%20particularly%20the%20JD(U)%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Shinde%20faction)%2C%20were%20equally%20sharp.%20The%20Congress%20had%20hyped%20Priyanka's%20maiden%20speech%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmoment%20the%20world%20has%20been%20waiting%20for%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20her%20mention%20of%20the%20plight%20of%20apple%20farmers%20in%20Congress-ruled%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20combined%20with%20her%20carrying%20a%20bag%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CPalestine%E2%80%9D%20logo%2C%20sparked%20greater%20public%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20definition%20of%20%3Cem%3Etapasya%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20his%20version%20of%20the%20Eklavya%20story%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20but%20they%20did%20little%20to%20boost%20Congress's%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20wasn't%20any%20better%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc.%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20other%20Congress%20leaders%20ended%20up%20defending%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20a%2012-second%20video%20clip%20undo%20the%20damage%3F%20Seems%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C