on't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20burden%20on%20anyone%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20share%20a%20long%20history%20of%20conflict%20and%20extensive%20checks%20on%20her%20identity%20were%20conducted%20before%20her%20Indian%20nationality%20was%20confirmed%20in%20October.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734527820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ftvcj9hu_hamida-bano-twitter_625x300_18_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-a-youtube-video-helped-bring-an-indian-origin-woman-back-from-pakistan-7278467%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20was%20approached%20by%20a%20recruitment%20agent%20in%202022%20who%20offered%20to%20arrange%20her%20a%20job%20in%20Dubai.%20In%20return%2C%20the%20agent%20asked%20her%20to%20pay%2020%2C000%20rupees.%20However%2C%20instead%20of%20Dubai%2C%20she%20was%20brought%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20a%20city%20in%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-a-youtube-video-helped-bring-an-indian-origin-woman-back-from-pakistan-7278467%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress%20Anti-Ambedkar%2C%20Twisted%20My%20Words%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20Amid%20Massive%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Famit-shah%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20ferocious%20Congress-led%20maelstrom%20following%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fambedkar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmbedkar%20is%20the%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20quip%20in%20Parliament%20last%20night%20-%20counterattacked%20Wednesday%20evening%20by%20accusing%20his%20rivals%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Banti-Ambedkar%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Banti-Constitution%26quot%