)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20beyond%20the%20physical%20toll%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20even%20more%20insidious%20impact%3A%20the%20social%20stigma.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F212728%2Fpadmashri-winner-2020-usha-chaumar-manual-scavenging-india-untouchability-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManual%20scavengers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20often%20ostracised%2C%20their%20dignity%20eroded%20by%20a%20society%20that%20deems%20their%20work%20impure.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20those%20engaged%20in%20this%20work%20are%20often%20left%20with%20little%20hope%20for%20better%20job%20prospects%20or%20social%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20if%20technology%20could%20end%20not%20just%20the%20physical%20danger%20of%20this%20work%2C%20but%20also%20the%20centuries-old%20stigma%20attached%20to%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala-based%20startup%20Genrobotics%20promises%20to%20answer%20this%20question%20with%20Bandicoot%20%E2%80%94%20a%20machine%20designed%20to%20eliminate%20manual%20scavenging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20robotic%20solution%20to%20a%20dehumanising%20problem%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20four%20engineers%20%E2%80%94%20Arun%20George%2C%20Nikhil%20NP%2C%20Rashid%20K%2C%20and%20Govind%20MK%20%E2%80%94%20Genrobotics%E2%80%99%20flagship%20innovation%2C%20the%20Bandicoot%20robot%2C%20is%20named%20after%20a%20species%20of%20rats%20which%20is%20known%20to%20dig%20and%20live%20in%20tunnels%20underground.%20It%20is%20specifically%20designed%20to%20clean%20sewers%2C%20septic%20tanks%2C%20and%20manholes%20without%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bandicoot%20robot%20is%20designed%20to%20operate%20in%20narrow%2C%20confined%20spaces%2C%20which%20are%20typically%20difficult%20and%20dangerous%20for%20humans%20to%20navigate%20and%20consists%20of%20two%20main%20components%3A%20a%20stand%20unit%20and%20a%20robotic%20drone%20unit.%20The%20drone%20unit%20is%20lowered%20into%20the%20manhole%2C%20where%20it%20uses%20high-resolution%20cameras%20to%20scan%20the%20surroundings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20cameras%20help%20the%20operator%20monitor%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20manhole%20on%20a%2013-inch%20display%2C%20providing%20real-time%20footage%20of%20the%20environment.%20Once%20the%20operator%20identifies%20the%20waste%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20cleared%2C%20the%20Bandicoot%E2%80%99s%20multi-functional%20robotic%20arm%2C%20equipped%20with%20shovels%20and%20grabbing%20tools%2C%20is%20deployed%20to%20collect%20the%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fscaven_11zon-1734087660.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fscaven_11zon-1734087660.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fscaven_11zon-1734087660-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fscaven_11zon-1734087660-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fscaven_11zon-1734087660-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fscaven_11zon-1734087660-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-389386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMany%20sanitation%20workers%20are%20cramped%20into%20hazardous%20spaces.%20This%20puts%20their%20lives%20at%20risk%20while%20performing%20manual%20scavenging%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Flickr%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20robot%E2%80%99s%20four%20sturdy%20robotic%20legs%20ensure%2